Transform using a single file that contains the instructions

Usage:
  kojo single INFILE [--save DIR] [ARGS...]
  kojo single (-h|--help)

Options:
  -s --save DIR
    Save output to directory instead of printing

  -h --help
    Show this help

Parameters:
  INFILE
    Template to transform. The template should contain a YAML front matter with
    transformation instructions

  ARGS
    Optional key=value pairs

Examples:
  kojo single Dockerfile
  kojo single template.Dockerfile --save .
  kojo single template.Dockerfile --save output
  kojo single template.Dockerfile scale=2
